                  </table>
                  <paragraph>The container closure is not made with natural rubber latex. Non-PVC, Non-DEHP, Sterile. Protect from freezing. Store at <content styleCode="bold">20</content>° to <content styleCode="bold">25</content>°C (<content styleCode="bold">68</content>° to <content styleCode="bold">77</content>°F). [See USP Controlled Room Temperature].
